cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

The paper deals with real-time object recognition, tracking, and reconstruction using RGB-D cameras, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) categories. The system also uses semantic segmentation and instance-level recognition, which are related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper presents augmented reality applications, which are related to computer graphics (cs.GR).
